				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey all,
<br />

<br />
I know there are those people who always fret over the fact that they'll never have the plat to buy dragon scales or DotB, etc.
<br />

<br />
However, last night I made over 5k in plat looting Rockhopper hide in DSP.  A couple of hours killling and looting the Rockhoppers (who were dk blue to me at 52) and then selling them in the Bazaar while I sleep.  Bam!  Wake up loaded.  A few more days of this and hopefully I can rake in 20 to 30k in plat.
<br />

<br />
The Flawless and Superb are the big sellers.  One I sold for over 400pp each and the other for 250pp can't remember which ATM.  These are also very easy to Swarm.  Just wanted to let you guys know.  </span></td>
			</tr><tr>
