Heh, I am beginning to hate the hopper caves, seems like dr00ds cant understand that a level 60+ bard can indeed camp the entire cave...had some dr00d decide to help herself to the hoppers I was killin a few days back...wouldn'y have been so bad, but she decided that the best place to root them was in the middle of my swarm...
