				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't really want to give this away but.....
<br />

<br />
The Ravenous Nightstalker camp on Plane of Nightmare is a good place for money.  The beasties drop diamonds, raw diamonds and blue diamonds, and although the bazaar market seems a little flooded on FV server right now, even selling them to the vendor is a pretty penny, 238 for the blues, 190 for the others.  The stalkers also drop some cheaper stuff, fangs, tufts of fur, etc, which sell in the 5 pp range.
<br />

<br />
The exp is very good too, and it is a great place to practice swarm kiting, at least from what I have heard.  I mainly use the safer but slower charm one pet and have it fight 1 or maybe 2 others; everytime I have pulled the whole camp I end up getting adds from beyond the tree line, spiders and treants and blood ravens oh my!!  Nothing like racing to the zone with 3 percent health left with 8 stalkers, 3 trees, 2 spiders and a blood raven following you.  I know I need to practice that swarm kiting but right now going the easy route.
<br />

<br />
So can sometimes make 1 k an hour, and maybe more if diamonds are in demand on your server.
<br />

<br />
Safe hunting!!
<br />

<br />
Pericles Talechaser
<br />
(Just graduated) Troubador of the 58th Song
<br />
Firiona Vie server</span></td>
