As for me, I did my 40s in Tim. Deep swarming Spirocs and Raptors.  Spirocs is a shared camp (at least on my server it was) so I would only pull all of them if I was alone or there was only a necro pulling singles.  What I did was tell folks I was pulling everything and if they wanted one, send me a tell and then pull one or 4 off my swarm with range spells.  That worked well as none of the folks got unwanted aggro and I went along with a slightly smaller swarm.  No biggie, everyone happy.  Mostly. If I got a jerk, I had no problem letting them kill themselves.  Really pissed them off due to the fact Tim Deep is not a short CR. hehe
